</taxonomicName>
, male internal genitalia. A—lateral view; B—ventral view; C—hypoproct, lateral view; Dpregonite, lateral view; E—postgonite, lateral view. Abbreviations: aa—aedeagal apodeme, ea—ejaculatory apodeme.
